overview:
JE Capital Fund LLP is a private investment firm focused on high investment returns in companies with long-term competitive advantages, and significant barriers to entry.

It provides a platform for opportunities that arises in the midst of the rapidly growing Chinese economy.

As an industry innovator, their motto is ” Be Bold to think ahead and act quickly”.

Headquartered in Singapore, with offices in China, Dubai, Hong Kong, India, Japan, Korea, Macau, Malaysia, Taiwan, USA, UK and The Netherland, working with market-leading companies by creating sustainable country focused investment platforms benefiting from the high growth prospects in the following areas:

Infrastructure Natural Resources Buyout Business services Industrials Consumer & Leisure Media & Technology Business Services Financial Services Development Capital Healthcare Acquisitions with Management
